snippet.title: ((AMBER ALERT TEXAS)) ISSUED FOR ABDUCTED 14 YEAR OLD GIRL
snippet.description:
((AMBER ALERT TEXAS))
AN AMBER ALERT WATCH IS IN EFFECT AT THIS TIME FOR THE ENTIRE STATE OF TEXAS..
AN AMBER ALERT WARNING IS NOW IN EFFECT FOR THE FOLLOWING STATES OKLAHOMA ARKANSAS AND LOUISIANA I REPEAT AN AMBER ALERT WARNING IS NOW IN EFFECT FOR THE FOLLOWING STATES OKLAHOMA ARKANSAS AND LOUISIANA

The MT. PLEASANT POLICE DEPARTMENT is searching for RUBY ZAVALA, Hispanic, Female, 14 years old, DOB 08/31/98, height 5 FT, weight 120 POUNDS, BLACK Hair, BROWN Eyes, wearing WHITE TOP, BLUE JEANS, TAN SHOES. Police are looking for JESUS RAMIREZ, Hispanic, Male, 22 years old, DOB 11/30/89, height 5 FT 9 IN, weight 165, BLACK Hair, BROWN Eyes, wearing BLACK BALL CAP. The suspect was last heard from in EAST 1ST ST., MT. PLEASANT. Law enforcement officals believe this child to be in grave or immediate danger. If you have any information regarding this abduction contact the MT. PLEASANT POLICE DEPARTMENT at 903-575-4004 News Media Point of Contact is MT. PLEASANT POLICE DEPARTMENT at 903-575-4004
